    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Another thing that seems broken about the menu widget (and may be related):\r\nIf you add a refinement, the search results are properly filtered, but the menu widget's active style is not applied to the facet value.\r\n\r\nIn this example, \"Music\" should be bold, but isn't: https://jsfiddle.net/timkelty/u766n8ah/\r\nNotice how the active state is set for the refinementList widget, but not for menu.\r\n",
