  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I don't really see the use case of manually setting `facets` for a managed facet. facets already merges with the existing parameters set by widgets, and in almost all cases, these parameters sound involved enough to be part of a custom widget instead of using solely configure, as there would be rendering involved too.\r\n\r\nI'll close this issue now, but if anyone else in the future has a similar issue, please open a new issue with reproduction. Thanks for opening!",
